    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The thick, brown, uncrystallized syrup drained from raw sugar, particularly the concentrated syrup obtained from sugar during the process of refining from cane or beet juice. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
